{"tid":2110683,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"夏千福等9位前美駐港領事聯署 促美國會向港人提供政治庇護","createTime":"2020-07-16T05:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T06:22:23.000Z","uid":48083,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e61c36a71e2c0beb9e0ba35911bc8209359c425e","tid":2110683,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"繼美國總統特朗普簽署《香港自治法案》，宣佈移除美國對香港的特殊待遇後，有報道指，9位前駐港美國總領事和十多位前國務院官員去信美國國會，促請國會向香港人提供政治庇護，更表明支持美國參眾兩會議員提出的《香港安全港法案（Hong Kong Safe Harbor Act）》，聯署人包括前總領事夏千福和唐偉康等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/YMEHG3HDAJSDUOGSCJCYGJ7RW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FYMEHG3HDAJSDUOGSCJCYGJ7RW4%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=ed61e13b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FYMEHG3HDAJSDUOGSCJCYGJ7RW4%2F&h=e70e1191\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/YMEHG3HDAJSDUOGSCJCYGJ7RW4/</a>"},{"pid":"69c0b7c1a2bda48bdabbaf3f0ab1ecda5a77104d","tid":2110683,"uid":95138,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a24203628e9cca129d968d514f85d9b3c064e9a5","tid":2110683,"uid":36432,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"God Bless America<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef38daa7017d84b239adcb1db8a02dc2d959b00","tid":2110683,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"未見有原文睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/07/15/china-hong-kong-trump-congress-former-us-officials-urge-refugee-status/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignpolicy.com%2F2020%2F07%2F15%2Fchina-hong-kong-trump-congress-former-us-officials-urge-refugee-status%2F&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n3%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=f27d0f77\" target=\"_blank\">https://foreignpolicy.com/2020/07/15/china-hong-kong-trump-congress-former-us-officials-urge-refugee-status/</a>"},{"pid":"ae3a14139fd3ddb899cf57af6867d6205b19add0","tid":2110683,"uid":259088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"借個位 保安局發出超過20萬張豁免強制檢疫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2106369/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2106369/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家支持廣傳消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔自救大家玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">我哋可以做咩嘢？</span></span></strong><br />\n1.話比身邊嘅人知香港有個後門大量吸收潛在冇病症感染者及傳播者。<br />\n<br />\n2.呼籲身邊所有人戴口罩，特別係果班唔肯帶嘅中年人<br />\n<br />\n3.如果身邊有料，可以報上傳媒比如蘋果。<br />\n例如喺之前post有其他人話知道：<br />\n灣仔入境個邊D移民公司而家當免檢疫証明係生意咁做，搵班阿姐派傳單幫人攪。<br />\n每日中港司機都幾千人出出入入。<br />\n<br />\n4.煲大件事！比全世界多D人知道，只有多D人覺醒，知道個政府係棄全香港巿民安危不顧，先會爭取到更多人企係我哋呢邊，同我哋一齊抗疫！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟姊妹各自爬山 他日平安相聚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b3c12ede332e2d1c9fee2936fadc07de75183c","tid":2110683,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"夏千福之前好似話一國兩制乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74d9171814b5aac4fa15639e5fbe2863281dbe3f","tid":2110683,"uid":100337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T05:50:16.000Z","msg":"挑戰明將嘅總領事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7eef369bd8332c79860cf704cdda953dd1624d7","tid":2110683,"uid":302348